episodes.title: Doug Scott Kramer on being free from Scientology.
episodes.description:
Doug Scott Kramer talks about his journey through and away from Scientology in order to break free from the church, discusses  manipulation techniques, how he managed to get out of the church and what impact this has had on his life. 

Doug's awesome YouTube Channel can be found here:
https://www.youtube.com/@dbnc/videos
